CodeList.Name: Coronary Artery Dominance

Description.TranslatedText: A codelist to describe the pattern of the epicardial vessels supplying the posterior descending artery and the posterolateral branches.

EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: The right coronary artery supplies the posterior descending artery and the circumflex supplies the posterolateral branches.
The left circumflex artery supplies the posterior descending artery and the posterolateral branches.
The right coronary artery supplies the posterior descending artery and the posterolateral branches.
